        <h2 class='db1 sectTitle'>Earshot</a></h2>
        <div class='slideshow'>
            <div class='mySlides0'>
                <img class='slideImg' src="../images/performance/earshot/2.Earshot.jpg">
                <p class='caption'>Strangers sit across from each other, listening to the characters through localized electronic speakers (Earshot, 2015, Bonnie Vee Bar, New York, NY). [1/8]</p>
            </div>
            <div class='mySlides0'>
                <img class='slideImg' src="../images/performance/earshot/1.Earshot.jpg">
