        <p class='bodyText'>A researcher at a biochemistry lab becomes infected with an unknown fungal disease, transforming into The Creature, a restless, impulsive, mischievous urchin. The Creature leaves the comfort of its rainbow fungal abode to spread its colorful spores onto the sterile spaces we all inhabit.</p>
        <p class='bodyText'>Documentation by Zach Bell and Andrew Wagner.</p>
